net.cloud.server.file.address

Class AddressConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.file.address.AddressConstants

  • public class AddressConstants
extends Object
    A class which contains constants that can be used for creation of a FileAddress.
    A SPACE_xxx constant essentially refers to the folder the file is in.
    An EXT_xxx constant is just for a file format. These are here... just because.
